Subject: Cannot access Reporting
Description: We've encountered this during ongoing attempts to solve prior ticket, but were are looking to migrate some SMB shares and now need to access Reports
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Users are able to log in to the Published Reports, but receive a 500 error after logging in and are unable to actually view the reports

[Resolution]
Added the NEA service account used for the AIC to the Pre-Windows 2000 Compatible Access group which has read access on all users and groups in the domain
